To support High Availability (HA) Grafana just need an external database where store dashboards, users and other persistent data. To configure the external database provide a configuration file containing the [database section](https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/installation/configuration/#database) of Grafana official documentation. For more information on Grafana High Availability, check out the following [documentation](https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/tutorials/ha_setup/).
